name: Mulan
info: Main character, the heroine of a Chinese poem who went to war with her elderly father, despite the fact that only men were taken into the army

name: Mushu
info: Mushu is boastful, overly witty and ready to do anything to achieve his goal. However, in difficult times he will always come to the rescue.

name: Li Shang
info: Shang is a very serious person. So he is trying to prove that he is capable of commanding not because his father is a general, but because he himself is worthy of it.

name: Fa Zu
info: He is Mulan's father and a former soldier

name: Fa Li
info: She is Mulan's mother and housewife

name: Grandma Fa
info: She is Mulan's grandmother and she gave Mulan a cricket

name: Khan
info: Main antagonist. He is the evil leader of the Hun army, responsible for mass genocide throughout China.
